Yvonne Monlaur https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Yvonne_Monlaur 0 Yvonne Monlaur (born Yvonne-Thérèse-Marie-Camille Bédat de Monlaur; 15 December 1939 – 18 April 2017) was a French film actress of the late 1950s and 1960s best known for her roles in the Hammer horror films.
